520
00:38:29,598 --> 00:38:30,641
Wait.

521
00:38:34,270 --> 00:38:35,706
- Whoa.
- Hold out your hand.

522
00:38:35,730 --> 00:38:36,772
Huh?

523
00:38:41,819 --> 00:38:42,987
Hold out your hand.

524
00:38:46,198 --> 00:38:49,452
